The paper focuses on evaluating the quality of a voice-based Q&A platform for knowledge sharing, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques (cs.CL, cs.IR). The dataset introduced in the paper can also be used for research in social computing (cs.SI), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
